column16: Lucas Duda walks.   Daniel Murphy to 2nd.
Daniel Murphy singles on a ground ball to center fielder Justin Ruggiano.   Juan Lagares to 3rd.
B.  J.   Upton flies out softly to center fielder Christian Yelich.
Julio Teheran out on a sacrifice bunt, catcher Rob Brantly to second baseman Donovan Solano.   Elliot Johnson to 2nd.
Elliot Johnson singles on a sharp ground ball to third baseman Ed Lucas.
Denard Span singles on a ground ball to first baseman Logan Morrison.
Jhonatan Solano flies out to right fielder Justin Ruggiano in foul territory.
Anthony Rendon grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Logan Morrison.
